      "1": {
        "type": "markdown",
        "content": "# 🏥 HonorHealth — CIO Executive Command Center\n---\n**Real-Time Observability | 9 Acute-Care Hospitals | 20,000+ Employees | $4B+ Health System**\n\n*Unified Technology Operations • Infrastructure • Applications • Security — Powered by Dynatrace*"
